## Khởi Động Docker

```bash
# Mở Docker Desktop trước, sau đó:
cd Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026\Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026
docker compose up -d

# Tạo initial migration:
dotnet ef migrations add InitialCreate --project Vns.Erp.Infrastructure --startup-project Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026
dotnet ef database update --project Vns.Erp.Infrastructure --startup-project Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026
```

| Service | URL |
|---|---|
| PostgreSQL | `localhost:5432` (user: `vns_erp`, pass: `VnsErp@2026!`) |
| pgAdmin | `localhost:5050` (email: `admin@vns.com.vn`, pass: `Admin@2026!`) |

